title: Bubble Shooter Premium Edition
description:
Bubble Shooter Premium Edition is a brand new version of the
famous Bubble Shooter game! Your goal is simple - shoot bubbles,
match three or more to blow them up and clear the game board!
Shoot big groups of bubbles of the same color to succeed, but if
you miss your target, a new row of bubbles will be added! Master
your skills and compete with players from all over the world in
multiplayer mode or try Underwater, Gems or Classic single-player
modes. It&#039;s tons of bubble popping fun!
